
** Requirements

  - instantclient-sqlplus-macosx-10.1.0.3.zip
  - instantclient-sdk-macosx-10.1.0.3.zip
  - instantclient-jdbc-macosx-10.1.0.3.zip
  - instantclient-basic-macosx-10.1.0.3.zip

** Directory to Installation

  - /opt/oracle/10.1.0/client (ORACLE_HOME)

** TNSNAMES.ORA

  - In $ORACLE_HOME/network/admin

** EZCONNECT

Seems not to work!!!

** ActivePerl

  - /usr/local/ActivePerl-5.8/

** Environment

  - DYLD_LIBRARY_PATH = $ORACLE_HOME

** DBD::Oracle

Do not use the normal procedure with "make" and "make install". This
changes the Make-Environment and then the second call to "make test"
or "make install" will fail.

  - perl.ppc Makefile.PL
  - make install

